                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-6">
                <h3 class="text-dark text-uppercase ml-5 text-center">Property Consultancy</h3>
                <img src="/img/consult.jpg" alt="Property Consultancy" class="img-thumbnail ml-3" width="550">
                <p class="text-dark ml-4">
                    We give professional advice on your property investments to yield maximum return.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row mt-5">
            <div class="col-lg-6">
                <h3 class="text-dark text-uppercase ml-5 text-center">Building construction</h3>
                <img src="/img/construction.jpg" alt="Building construction" class="img-thumbnail ml-3" width="520">
